%%
%% SecureTrack — UML Sequence: pipeline blocks a vulnerable commit (3 iters)
%%
%% This is THE money diagram for the defense:
%%   - Iteration 1: Gitleaks blocks (V1, V2 hardcoded secrets)
%%   - Iteration 2: Semgrep blocks (V3 SQL injection)
%%   - Iteration 3: All gates green → SBOM + Cosign sign + ECS deploy + ZAP
%%
%% Each iteration corresponds to a real commit on the `hardened` branch, so the
%% jury can replay the narrative from `git log --oneline`.
%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Dev as Developer
    participant Repo as GitHub Repo
    participant GA as GitHub Actions
    participant GL as Gitleaks
    participant SG as Semgrep
    participant SC as SonarCloud
    participant TV as Trivy
    participant HD as Hadolint
    participant CT as Conftest/OPA
    participant ECR as Amazon ECR
    participant CO as Cosign + Fulcio
    participant ECS as ECS Fargate
    participant ZAP as OWASP ZAP

    Note over Dev,ZAP: Iteration 1 — Secret detected
    Dev->>Repo: git push (hardcoded secret + SQLi)
    Repo->>GA: webhook trigger
    GA->>GL: scan repo
    GL-->>GA: 2 secrets found (V1, V2)
    Note over GA: Gate 1 BLOCK
    GA-->>Repo: PR check fail + comment

    Note over Dev,ZAP: Iteration 2 — SAST catches SQLi
    Dev->>Repo: push fix (remove secrets)
    Repo->>GA: re-trigger
    GA->>GL: scan
    GL-->>GA: clean
    GA->>SG: SAST
    SG-->>GA: SQL injection (V3)
    Note over GA: Gate 2 BLOCK

    Note over Dev,ZAP: Iteration 3 — All green, deploy + verify
    Dev->>Repo: push fix (parameterized query)
    Repo->>GA: re-trigger
    GA->>GL: ok
    GA->>SG: ok
    GA->>SC: code quality
    SC-->>GA: quality gate passed
    GA->>TV: SCA + image scan
    TV-->>GA: no critical CVEs
    GA->>HD: lint Dockerfile
    HD-->>GA: ok
    GA->>CT: policy validation
    CT-->>GA: ok
    GA->>ECR: docker push
    GA->>CO: sign image (OIDC keyless)
    CO-->>GA: signature + Rekor entry
    GA->>ECS: aws ecs update-service
    ECS-->>GA: deployment OK + healthcheck 200
    GA->>ZAP: baseline scan against ALB URL
    ZAP-->>GA: no high findings
    GA-->>Repo: PR check pass + summary + Grafana link
